<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Withdrawal Declined</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .details-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .details-table th, .details-table td {
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .details-table th {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      color: #555;
    }
    .reason {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #e74c3c;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #fce4e4;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>247AT</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= firstName %>,</p>
      <p>We regret to inform you that your recent withdrawal request has been declined. Below are the details:</p>
      
      <table class="details-table">
        <tr>
          <th>Amount</th>
          <td>$<%= withdrawalDetails.amount %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Broker Fee</th>
          <td>$<%= withdrawalDetails.brokerFee %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Status</th>
          <td><%= withdrawalDetails.status %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Request Date</th>
          <td><%= withdrawalDetails.createdAt %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <div class="reason">
        Reason: <%= reason %>
      </div>
      <p>If you believe this was a mistake or have any questions, please contact our support team for assistance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The 247AT Team</p>
      <p>Â© <span id="current-year"></span> 247AT. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('current-year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>